songs.title: ZCAMMER’S ANTHEM
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Diablo on the beat, nigga
I got the devil with the heat, nigga

[Hook]
Swipe, swipe, take your face then take your life
Swipe, swipe, all my niggas bustin' pipe
Swipe, swipe, Swiper, no swipin'
I'm the shit, I'm the shit, no wipin'
Swipe, swipe, take your face then take your life
Swipe, swipe, all my niggas bustin' pipe
Swipe, swipe, Swiper, no swipin'
I'm the shit, I'm the shit, no wipin'

[Verse 1]
Aye, fuck demons, nigga!
I just want a bad bitch to suck my semen, nigga
Aye, these niggas schemin', nigga
Runnin' through you niggas
Got me think you dreamin' nigga
Aye, got Diablo, Pablo
I'm at the car show, cargo
It's suicidal, revival
